      "id": "PopularPost255902",
      "post_content": "I feel like cards like this are vastly under valued. Card vaue is typically determined by a cards deck synergy and its immediate impact on the board via removal or card drawing etc. I would say this defender card does have an immediate impact as it immediately forces your opponent to evaluate their tactics. The presence of a dedicated and hearty blocker forces your opponent to draw go or waste removal to make their attacks make any worthwhile gain without just leaving themselves open.   \n  \nThat said this card not only provides that kind of presence, it buffs your primary attacker (another cool thing about the Exalted mechanic is that it can make any card on your board a threat and your opponent won't even know which one until its swinging). Though down a [Builder's Blessing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Builder's Blessing) and this guy is cable of stopping some of the biggest threats from the new core (including the new mythic rare dragon) assuming you can give it flying or reach some how.",
      "posted_by": "alphagprime",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost255902\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I feel like cards like this are vastly under valued. Card vaue is typically determined by a cards deck synergy and its immediate impact on the board via removal or card drawing etc. I would say this defender card does have an immediate impact as it immediately forces your opponent to evaluate their tactics. The presence of a dedicated and hearty blocker forces your opponent to draw go or waste removal to make their attacks make any worthwhile gain without just leaving themselves open. <br/><br/>That said this card not only provides that kind of presence, it buffs your primary attacker (another cool thing about the Exalted mechanic is that it can make any card on your board a threat and your opponent won't even know which one until its swinging). Though down a <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Builder's Blessing\">Builder's Blessing</a> and this guy is cable of stopping some of the biggest threats from the new core (including the new mythic rare dragon) assuming you can give it flying or reach some how.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy78921\">alphagprime</span>\r\n         