      "id": "PopularPost267141",
      "post_content": "Strong defender with a great mechanic that it seems people are constantly undervaluing.   \n  \nStrong turn three defender with Exalted that belongs to TWO strong tribes ([Champion of the Parish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Champion of the Parish) likes this; so does [Elder Cathar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elder Cathar) and [Captain of the Watch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Captain of the Watch), among others) = solid card, no question.  \n  \nAnd the art is interesting, makes you look closely at it to see what's what. I like that, too.",
